 internationalbribery scandalinvolving Salt Lake City's 2002 bid.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999975471624181, \"rank\": 2.4528435549935005e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 992, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.6731821138495908, \"rank\": 0.45717968133790804, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacques_Rogge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rogge\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q30461\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacques_Rogge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacques_Rogge\"}, {\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9995375496002841, \"rank\": 0.0004626638089267062, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic fencer\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the term limits\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"the charter\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"reforms\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1990s\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"the internationalbribery\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1188}]}, {