: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9996325344566022, \"rank\": 0.00022702850062729775, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some issues\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"their country's invasion\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last October, Bach was publicly encouraged by some IOC members to support changing the rules on term limits and seek four more years as president through 2029.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999975471624181, \"rank\": 2.4528435549935005e-06, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3799462938623566e-26, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"term limits\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"four more years\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While he did not dismiss running again, Bach did make it clear the election should not disrupt the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2055, \"